title: ReConnect.exe
description: This software is a special help for users with dial-up connections or users who need to connect with a username and password to the internet using the Wizard from Windows.So...it can automatically start at your computer start-up and connect your network conection 100% automatically.But..there&#039;s more...when your Internet Conection drops...it automatically reconnects it in seconds!.And if this does not happen in second the programs tries to connect untill you&#039;re connected to the Internet.
